<Base title="Affiliate Disclosure" description="Affiliate disclosure.">
  <h1>Affiliate Disclosure</h1>
  <p>Some of the outbound links on this site are affiliate or referral links. If you click one and sign up for a paid plan, we may earn a commission at no extra cost to you.</p>
  <p>Affiliate revenue does not influence our rankings, which are computed automatically from each provider's public pricing data. We do not accept payment for inclusion or placement.</p>
  <p>If you would prefer to use a non-referral link, every provider page also includes the provider's homepage URL in the footer of the table.</p>
</Base>
